      "date": "2013-04-09 20:55:20.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\n(Style) should use $(...) instead of `...`\n\n(Style) should localize variables in test\n\nIt also isn't necessary to use openfile to create a file without stripes, mknod will also work. I suspect the test may not actually be hitting the problem, since the lfs process will open the file and create stripes on the file before calling the ioctl.",
